reviews.reviewbody: when i was in second year high school, we're required to read KANGKONG.. at first i thought it was the most boring book but while reading it i realize that it's wery good.. when i finished it i realized that it was one of the best book i've ever read.. a teenager can make a difference in this world.. i suggest everyone to read it..? peace
